_code,status_message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,4,context deadline exceeded,出现次数:1\n", "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-10T18:10:08Z to 2025-06-10T18:23:08Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-10 18:10:08+00:00 to 2025-06-10 18:23:08+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "基于对日志数据的全面扫描，我发现了显著的异常模式。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"AdService--gc\", \"GCHelper\", \"InvocationTargetException\", \"Byteman agent\", \"DeadlineExceeded\", \"context deadline exceeded\", \"gc\", \"failed to get ads\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman GC故障注入导致服务性能严重下降，触发频繁GC操作\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService--gc-1749579009 execute() 出现次数155次，byteman gc helper trigger gc，Rule.execute called for AdService--gc-1749579009\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"由于adservice的GC故障导致RPC调用超时，frontend无法获取广告数据\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **主要异常**：adservice服务遭受了Byteman工具的GC故障注入攻击，触发了大量GC操作\n2. **影响范围**：所有3个adservice实例（adservice-0, adservice-1, adservice-2）都受到影响\n3. **连锁反应**：frontend服务因adservice性能下降而出现RPC调用超时错误\n4. **故障模式**：这是典型的性能故障注入场景，GC操作频繁执行导致服务响应延迟\n\n**故障根因**：adservice的GC故障注入是系统故障的主要根源，导致服务间调用超时。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取的调用链数据，我现在进行全面的异常分析。让我仔细分析这些异常调用链和错误状态。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->shippingservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice内部调用异常：EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation延迟从24.5s增加到80.8s(3.3倍)，ShippingService/GetQuote从9.4s增加到36.2s(3.8倍)，PaymentService/Charge从13.9s增加到45.4s(3.3倍)，CartService/EmptyCart从20.2s增加到73.8s(3.7倍)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice调用cartservice的GetCart操作延迟显著增加：从2.0s增加到8.0s(4.0倍)，另一实例从2.5s增加到42.1s(16.6倍)，checkoutservice内部GetCart调用也从8.2s增加到14.4s\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用AdService/GetAds出现context deadline exceeded错误，同时延迟从5.5s增加到41.5s(7.5倍)，表明adservice可能不可用或响应超慢\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend直接调用ShippingService/GetQuote延迟从201ms增加到285ms，另一实例从205ms增加到565ms，同时checkoutservice内部调用ShipOrder从14.4s增加到74.3s(5.2倍)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用ListProducts延迟从72.7ms增加到224ms(3.1倍)，recommendationservice调用延迟从75.2ms增加到117.8ms，表明productcatalogservice响应变慢\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用CheckoutService/PlaceOrder延迟异常降低(从154.7s降到74.9s)，可能表明前端出现fast fail或熔断机制触发\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n\n1. **最严重的延迟问题**出现在checkoutservice内部调用的多个下游服务，特别是cartservice的GetCart操作延迟增加了16.6倍。\n\n2. **明确的错误状态**：adservice出现context deadline exceeded错误，表明该服务可能完全不可用。\n\n3. **系统性延迟**：几乎所有服务的响应时间都显著增加，表明可能存在底层基础设施问题或级联故障。\n\n4. **调用链根因分析**：由于多个服务同时出现延迟和错误，需要进一步分析是否存在共同的依赖问题（如网络、数据库连接等）。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于对故障期间指标数据的全面扫描分析，我发现了多个显著的异常调用链和资源问题。以下是初始扫描阶段的发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存使用率异常飙升，node_memory_usage_rate从32.29%上升到51.91%（变化率46.6%），可用内存node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes从11GB减少到7.7GB\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: 32.29% → 51.91% (+46.6%), node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: 11GB → 7.7GB (-35.1%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"服务错误率异常，error_ratio和client_error_ratio的P99值从0%飙升到19.55%，表明该Pod出现严重错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio P99: 0.0% → 19.55% (+200%), client_error_ratio P99: 0.0% → 19.55% (+200%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"最大响应时间rrt_max显著恶化，P99值从10.3ms飙升到90.98ms（变化率159.3%），位于内存异常的aiops-k8s-04节点上\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max P99: 10.3ms → 90.98ms (+159.3%), 位于aiops-k8s-04节点\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"最大响应时间rrt_max异常变化，中位数从42.99ms下降到10.24ms但P99值从49.26ms下降到34.03ms，可能存在性能波动\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max median: 42.99ms → 10.24ms (-123%), P99: 49.26ms → 34.03ms (-36.6%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-06\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存使用率上升，node_memory_usage_rate从26.73%上升到33.77%（变化率23.3%），存在资源压力\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: 26.73% → 33.77% (+23.3%)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n1. **节点级问题**：aiops-k8s-04节点内存使用率大幅上升，可能是系统故障的主要触发点\n2. **服务级异常**：cartservice-1出现高错误率，currencyservice-1响应时间显著恶化\n3. **关联性分析**：currencyservice-1恰好位于内存异常的aiops-k8s-04节点上，可能存在资源竞争关系\n4. **性能波动**：多个服务出现响应时间异常，但变化幅度相对较小\n\n需要进一步深入分析以确定根因组件和故障模式。"}
